Class InternalLogger

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.cloudbees.syslog.util.InternalLogger

  • public class InternalLogger
extends Object
    Don't use Logger as this code can be used as an Handler for java.util.logging and we would then have an infinite loop.

    Cyrille Le Clerc
